@startuml IoT Telemetry Infrastructure

title Figure 2 - IoT Telemetry Infrastructure Architecture

package "Data Sources" {
  [IoT Sensors\n(10,000 devices)] as sensors
  [Edge Gateways] as gateways
}

package "Ingestion Layer" {
  [Apache Kafka\n(Cluster)] as kafka
  [Kafka Streams] as kstreams
  [MQTT Broker] as mqtt
}

package "Storage Layer" {
  package "Time-Series Database" {
    [InfluxDB] as influx
    [TimescaleDB] as timescale
  }
  
  package "Data Lake" {
    [Raw Parquet Files] as raw
    [Aggregated Data] as aggregated
  }
  
  package "Hot Storage" {
    [Redis TimeSeries] as redis
  }
}

package "Processing Layer" {
  [Stream Processing\n(Window Aggregations)] as stream_proc
  [Anomaly Detection\n(ML Model)] as anomaly
  [Batch Aggregation\n(Daily/Hourly)] as batch
}

package "Serving Layer" {
  [Time-Series API] as ts_api
  [Alerting Service] as alerts
  [Dashboards\n(Grafana)] as dashboards
  [Historical API] as history_api
}

' Data flow
sensors --> mqtt : MQTT protocol (every 5s)
gateways --> kafka : Batched telemetry
mqtt --> kafka : Protocol bridge

' Real-time processing
kafka --> stream_proc : Raw telemetry stream
stream_proc --> redis : Real-time aggregates (1min)
stream_proc --> influx : Detailed data points
stream_proc --> anomaly : Anomaly detection

' Anomaly handling
anomaly --> alerts : Trigger alerts
anomaly --> kafka : Anomaly events

' Storage strategy
influx --> raw : Downsample to Parquet (daily)
redis --> aggregated : Cache recent aggregates
batch --> aggregated : Historical aggregates

' Serving
influx --> ts_api : Recent data queries
timescale --> history_api : Historical queries
redis --> dashboards : Real-time metrics
aggregated --> dashboards : Historical trends
ts_api --> dashboards : Custom queries

note right: 
  **Storage Strategy:**
  - **Hot (Redis):** Last 24h, sub-second access
  - **Warm (InfluxDB):** 30 days detailed
  - **Cold (Data Lake):** 1+ year aggregated
  
  **Processing:**
  - Window: 1min, 5min, 1h aggregations
  - Anomaly: Statistical + ML-based
end note

legend right
  |=Legend|=|
  |<#32CD32> Real-time Flow</color>|
  |<#4169E1> Batch Flow</color>|
  |<#FF6347> Alert Flow</color>|
endlegend

@enduml
